## events.rpy
## Daily event definitions and dispatch logic.
## Events are called randomly during the day_loop in script.rpy.

## ── MORNING EVENTS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

label event_morning:

    narrator "The morning sun rises over the camp, casting long shadows across the dew-covered grass."

    return

## ── AFTERNOON EVENTS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

label event_afternoon:

    narrator "The afternoon heat makes everyone seek shade under the tall pine trees by the lake."

    return

## ── EVENING EVENTS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

label event_evening:

    narrator "As dusk settles, campers gather around the crackling campfire, sharing stories under the stars."

    return
